# Premium Gastro Communication Hub - Environment Configuration
# Most secrets are stored in 1Password (vault: AI) and should be retrieved using the `op` CLI
# For local development: cp env.example .env and use 1Password references or actual values

# ===========================================
# CORE DATABASE & SECURITY
# ===========================================
DB_PASSWORD=your_strong_database_password_here
N8N_PASSWORD=your_n8n_admin_password_here
N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY=your_32_character_encryption_key_here

# ===========================================
# TWILIO & WHATSAPP (REQUIRED FOR SETUP)
# ===========================================
# Get these from: https://console.twilio.com/
